ehrte und wissenschaftliche Poetik auch über 'sich selbst' aufklärt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGerman poetryxHistory and criticism. 0aLiteraturexAesthetics. 0aPoeticsxHistory. 0aPoetics. 0aPoetry. 4aDeutsch. 4aPoetologische Lyrik. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2008z9783110212129oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2008z9783110209457oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311017760240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311020191840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110201918423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110201918/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2008  aZDB-23-DGGb2008  aZDB-23-GLCc2000d2014